name: Solify100
description: Solify100 is a transformative crypto project that integrates emotional wellness tools with financial innovation. Built on the Solana blockchain, Solify100 aims to create a compassionate and empowering ecosystem driven by AI agents, market sentiment intelligence, and a robust rewards system. Solify100's mission is to go beyond the meme coin narrative and shape a community-centric movement grounded in mental health and shared growth.
